# description

Senior-level coding standards for building modern, scalable React and Next.js applications using **TypeScript**, **Chakra UI** for all components and UI structure, and **Tailwind CSS** for layout utilities like spacing and responsiveness. This rule ensures clean, DRY, accessible, and production-ready code with no unfinished logic or TODOs.

